abstract: She surveyed the media landscape and decided that truth was what she said it was.
snippet: She surveyed the media landscape and decided that truth was what she said it was.
lead_paragraph: Bret Stephens: Gail, I know you are as gutted as I am by the news that Sarah Huckabee Sanders will step down from her post as White House spokesman. How do you judge her contribution to our nationâ€™s moral health and political well-being?
